                <div type="textpart" n="b">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><persName ref="#asteria">Ennia Asteria</persName>, <persName ref="#asterius">Enni Asteri</persName> filia,
                        <lb n="2"/>ex origine <persName ref="#cerealis">Enni Cerealis</persName> avi sui arcam
                        <lb n="3"/>suo nomine renovavit, quam post ex
                        <lb n="4" break="no"/>cessum suum si quis <choice><reg>irrumperit</reg><orig>inruperit</orig></choice> inferet fisci
                        <lb n="5"/>rationibus <measure type="fine" unit="sestertius" quantity="200"><choice><reg>sestertium</reg><orig>HS</orig></choice> <num value="200">CC</num> <choice><abbr>N</abbr><expan>N<ex>ummum</ex></expan></choice></measure>. Fili sane veniam habebunt.
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app loc="1a" from="#w1">
                        <lem>
                            
                        </lem>
                        <rdg source="#bertolini1877 #edr097935">
                            <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan>D<ex>is</ex></expan></choice> <choice><abbr>M</abbr><expan>M<ex>anibus</ex></expan></choice>
                        </rdg>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <p>
                        <persName ref="#asteria" xml:lang="la">Ennia Asteria</persName>, daughter of <persName ref="#asterius" xml:lang="la">Ennius Asterius</persName>, restored in her own name the arca that had belonged to her grandfather <persName ref="#cerealis" xml:lang="la">Ennius Cerealis</persName>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If anyone should violate it after her death, he shall pay two hundred sesterces to the accounts of the <term xml:lang="la">fiscus</term>. Her children, however, shall be exempt.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                    <p>
                        <persName ref="#asteria" xml:lang="la">Ennia Asteria</persName>, figlia di <persName ref="#asterius" xml:lang="la">Ennius Asterius</persName>, restaurò a suo nome l’arca che era stata del nonno <persName ref="#cerealis" xml:lang="la">Ennius Cerealis</persName>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Se qualcuno, dopo la sua morte, dovesse violarla, pagherà alle casse del <term xml:lang="la">fiscus</term> duecento sesterzi. I figli, tuttavia, ne saranno esentati.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
